source.name: CTA - Ridership - Bus Routes - Daily Totals by Route
source.description: This dataset shows total daily ridership on a per-route basis dating back to 2001. Daytypes are as follows: W=Weekday, A=Saturday, U=Sunday/Holiday. See attached readme file for more detailed information.
